OL,7,FThis game will mark the first match
OL,8,Fplayed in Wales since the Scottish
OL,9,Frugby legend and MND campaigner Doddy
OL,10,FWeir's death from the condition in
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FAs one of rugby's most recognisable
OL,14,Fpersonalities, Doddie Weir earned 61
OL,15,Fcaps for Scotland during his career.
OL,16,FBut in 2017, he revealed he was
OL,17,Fsuffering from MND.
