OL,4,CMotor Neurone Disease to deliver match
OL,5,Cball
OL,7,FUsing his platform to help others, he
OL,8,Flaunched the charity 'My Name'5 Doddie
OL,9,FFoundation' to help fellow sufferers
OL,10,Fand seek ways to further research into
OL,11,Fthis, as yet, incurable disease.
OL,13,FThe Wales v Scotland opener will mark
OL,14,Fthe climax of Doddie Aid 2024, an
OL,15,Fannual fundraiser organised by the
OL,16,Fcharity.
