OL,7,FDoddie Aid is a virtual mass-
OL,8,Fparticipation event conducted over a
OL,9,Ffive week period. Since its inception
OL,10,Fin 2020, the event has raised more
OL,11,Fthan #4 million for MND research.
OL,13,FAlmost 20,000 fundraisers have taken
OL,14,Fpart in this year's efforts with
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds
OL,16,Falready raised to help fund research
OL,17,Finto MND.
