OL,3,CWales v Scotland: Father-of-two with
OL,4,CMotor Neurone Disease to deliver match
OL,5,Cball
OL,7,FMark Williams and his young family
OL,8,Fhave been hailed "a beacon of light"
OL,9,Ffor others as he set his sights on
OL,10,Fraising money for the Doddie Aid.
OL,11,FThose who know Mr Williams in the
OL,12,FAbertillery community have praised him
OL,13,Ffor his refusal to be defined by the
OL,14,Flimitations and difficulties of the
OL,15,Fdisease.
OL,17,FIn defiance of his doctors, Mr
OL,18,FWilliams regularly exercises and even
OL,19,Fclimbed Pen-y-Fan in Bannau
OL,20,FBrycheiniog, the highest peak in South
OL,21,FWales.
