OL,3,CWales v Scotland: Father-of-two with
OL,4,CMotor Neurone Disease to deliver match
OL,5,Cball
OL,7,FHe said: "It will be a massive honour
OL,8,Fto hand over the match ball for the
OL,9,FDoddie Weir Cup, not only as a proud
OL,10,FWelsh rugby fan, but as an ambassador
OL,11,Ffor the importance of our continued
OL,12,Ffight against MND.
OL,14,F"Doddie Weir continues to be an
OL,15,Finspiration to the whole MND
OL,16,Fcommunity, showing everybody what's
OL,17,Fpossible even when facing this
OL,18,Fterrible disease."
