OL,3,CWales v Scotland: Father-of-two with
OL,4,CMotor Neurone Disease to deliver match
OL,5,Cball
OL,7,FHe continued: "The only way we can all
OL,8,Fprevent people in future facing the
OL,9,Fsame devastating diagnosis that I,
OL,10,FDoddie, and everybody with MND and
OL,11,Ftheir families had to go through is to
OL,12,Fraise money for research."
OL,14,FThe foundation's director, Paul
OL,15,FThompson, said: "The Doddie Weir Cup
OL,16,Fis always a symbol of the special bond
OL,17,Fbetween these nations, and now a
OL,18,Fcelebration of Doddie's life and the
OL,19,Fimpact his tireless campaigning
OL,20,Fcontinues to have."
