OL,7,FScott Quinnell, the British and Irish
OL,8,FLion and captain of Team Wales for
OL,9,FDoddie Aid, said: "Doddie Weir did so
OL,10,Fmuch for the MND community, using his
OL,11,Fprofile and personality to raise
OL,12,Fmillions for vital research."
OL,14,FHe added: "Mark is one of those who
OL,15,Fhas picked up the baton. What he's
OL,16,Fdone already has been absolutely
OL,17,Fincredible and he is an inspiration."
